; Coverage for post.cc lines 244-245 (get_price with annotation)
; and lines 226-228 (get_has_cost, get_cost with cost)
; Tests price extraction from annotated amounts.

2024/01/01 Buy
    Assets:Brokerage    10 AAPL @ $150.00
    Assets:Cash

test reg Assets:Brokerage --format "%(has_cost) %(price)\n"
true $1500
end test
